need to do:

1. Javafx Scene Builder download:
http://www.oracle.com/technetwork/java/javase/downloads/sb2download-2177776.html
note: eclipse must be 4.3 or greater(Luna) with Java JDK 8(includes JavaFX 8).

2. Add e(fx)clipse plugin:
Install:
http://www.eclipse.org/efxclipse/install.html
Specify the path to your Scene Builder executable: 
Open eclipse - Window - Preferences - JavaFX - enter you Scene Builder exe file path.

3.JavaFX with Scene Builder tutorial:
http://code.makery.ch/java/javafx-8-tutorial-part1/